== Comment following B-class assessment ==
Originally posted at [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Military history/Assessment/Requests]], but noting here as it may not have been seen before archiving.
The article meets the B-class criteria, but any steps towards higher article classifications should probably include a meatier lead section, and (if possible) an overview of the quantity, mix, and type of aircraft usually embarked, in addition to or instead of the case-by-case information provided in the ship history. -- [[User:Saberwyn|saberwyn]] 00:06, 7 January 2012 (UTC)
